{"tid":1474004,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搞死國泰，中國就控有全港航空既主導權","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:44.000Z","uid":10287,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a85e0fa100c7272b43955adcc66aa83102c50745","tid":1474004,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"我唔清楚成件事係咪會咁發展，雖然都會有其他外國airline 進出香港，但係邊到會夠國泰多。<br />\n<br />\n其一，收集個人資料，下次搞咩行動，你去邊到旅行都收集哂資料，預備加入黎緊果個社會信用體系<br />\n<br />\n其二，控制人口進出，有咩事停飛哂d機，外國airline 邊到接到咁多人離開香港<br />\n<br />\n其三，再次減少香港對外影響力，搞機場係焦土大家都明，但作為上市公司要為股民負責，除非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733ccb46c807f26a8608412123c70d1c877a54ef","tid":1474004,"uid":169497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"依個真 國泰唔死得"},{"pid":"7070c79b18618f5dcf841ce524969d7b4fce23e2","tid":1474004,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"oish"},{"pid":"d8afd9710b130d42239043d5787bafa4b69c8435","tid":1474004,"uid":282449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"e122b675d29e0efa583807f87bf74f190ffa253f","tid":1474004,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"18e43161b9772d4b554c0c270e1645d16d2467a8","tid":1474004,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd55b31dde240e5301348a37054f22b3ad1d039b","tid":1474004,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚再搞機場<br />\n<br />\n國泰已經好大鑊"},{"pid":"86fa61d917198ab706335521e0d531639d22c6fd","tid":1474004,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"入去睇睇 國泰唔死得<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/209641255886389/posts/1160786124105226?s=705840893&am